{"parentUuid":"783c5dad-af89-4e8b-976e-db95b8e3ec53","isSidechain":false,"userType":"external","cwd":"C:\\Users\\Administrator","sessionId":"6228359a-c661-44d6-9a1f-58764c0a7b14","version":"2.1.49","gitBranch":"HEAD","message":{"id":"msg_202602211959030bd7759872e44d46","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"glm-4.7","content":[{"type":"text","text":"我可以帮你了解如何将手机与电脑连接。你想要实现什么具体操作？\n\n以下是几种常见的手机连接方式：\n\n## 1. 通过 USB 数据线连接\n- **Android**：启用\"文件传输\"或\"USB 调试\"模式\n- **iPhone**：信任电脑后可在 iTunes/访达中访问\n\n## 2. 无线连接方式\n- **蓝牙**：适用于文件传输\n- **同一 Wi-Fi**：适用于各种投屏、同步工具\n- **二维码扫描**：快速配对\n\n## 3. 常用工具\n| 平台 | 工具 |\n|------|------|\n| Android | Scrcpy（投屏控制）、AirDroid、QtScrcpy |\n| iPhone | AirServer、LonelyScreen（AirPlay） |\n| 通用 | KDE Connect、LocalSend（文件传输） |\n| 跨平台 | 微信/钉钉、华为电脑管家等 |\n\n---\n\n请告诉我你具体想做什么？例如：\n- 投屏控制手机\n- 传输文件\n- 手机调试开发\n- 其他操作"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":18944,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":512,"output_tokens":231,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"type":"assistant","uuid":"5d5200f7-2b0f-48df-b3f1-6944692fcd73","timestamp":"2026-02-21T11:59:09.789Z"}
