{"parentUuid":"b0290cde-9c5e-4b96-8b41-4286dedfa2a3","isSidechain":false,"userType":"external","cwd":"C:\\Users\\Administrator","sessionId":"6228359a-c661-44d6-9a1f-58764c0a7b14","version":"2.1.49","gitBranch":"HEAD","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":"华为matex5典藏版"},"uuid":"0fa5a4cc-d671-4ea3-9a0e-1a1c74df43e3","timestamp":"2026-02-21T12:26:12.616Z","todos":[],"permissionMode":"default"}
{"parentUuid":"0fa5a4cc-d671-4ea3-9a0e-1a1c74df43e3","isSidechain":false,"userType":"external","cwd":"C:\\Users\\Administrator","sessionId":"6228359a-c661-44d6-9a1f-58764c0a7b14","version":"2.1.49","gitBranch":"HEAD","message":{"id":"msg_20260221202613c2c3b6b35c8f4ff7","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"glm-4.7","content":[{"type":"text","text":"华为 Mate X5 典藏版，按以下步骤操作：\n\n---\n\n**1. 检查音量和静音**\n- 按右侧音量+键，确保音量不是最低\n- 下拉控制中心，检查勿扰模式是否开启（月亮图标）\n\n---\n\n**2. 清理听筒/扬声器**\n- 听筒在屏幕顶部中间\n- 主扬声器在手机右侧（展开状态下屏幕右侧）\n- 用软毛刷轻扫，或用吹气球吹一下\n\n---\n\n**3. 检查智能协助设置**\n- 设置 → 智能辅助 → 智慧语音 → 确保\"静音时扬声器播放\"已开启\n\n---\n\n**4. 检查辅助功能**\n- 设置 → 辅助功能 → 无障碍 → 音频/听觉 → 检查是否有单声道音频等设置异常\n\n---\n\n**5. 重置所有设置**（不影响数据）\n- 设置 → 系统和更新 → 重置 → 重置所有设置\n\n---\n\n**6. 如果以上都不行**\n- 设置 → 系统和更新 → 软件更新 → 检查是否有系统更新\n- 去「我的华为」APP → 服务 → 预约维修（可能是硬件问题）\n\n---\n\n建议先按 **1-5** 步骤试一下，哪一步做了有变化吗？"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":24747,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":512,"output_tokens":287,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"type":"assistant","uuid":"43216ce5-6995-41c9-a7db-e931f49650c6","timestamp":"2026-02-21T12:26:19.015Z"}
