{"parentUuid":"b18ea96a-03c7-4b3e-ad1d-f55bfed618ee","isSidechain":false,"userType":"external","cwd":"C:\\Users\\Administrator","sessionId":"6228359a-c661-44d6-9a1f-58764c0a7b14","version":"2.1.49","gitBranch":"HEAD","message":{"id":"msg_2026022120322143bd1ca8b5aa4fe7","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"glm-4.7","content":[{"type":"text","text":"ADB 未安装。由于华为手机需要在手机上直接操作，请按以下步骤在手机上修复：\n\n---\n\n**立即修复方案**（在手机上操作）：\n\n**第一步：强制关闭音频服务**\n1. 设置 → 应用 → 应用管理 → 右上角「┆」→ 显示所有进程\n2. 搜索「音频」或「Audio」\n3. 找到「音频服务」或「MediaAudio」→ 强制停止\n\n**第二步：清除缓存分区**\n1. 关机\n2. 同时按住「电源键 + 音量+键」约10秒\n3. 进入 Recovery 模式 → 选择「清除缓存分区」\n4. 重启手机\n\n**第三步：重置声音设置**\n1. 设置 → 声音和振动\n2. 下拉到最底 → 高级设置\n3. 点击「重置声音设置」\n\n---\n\n**如果上面都不行**，最后方案：\n\n```\n设置 → 系统和更新 → 重置 → 恢复出厂设置\n```\n\n（记得先备份到华为云）\n\n---\n\n你现在能操作手机吗？按第一步试试。"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":78,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":26112,"output_tokens":241,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"type":"assistant","uuid":"d13a71ed-2b11-4a8c-b286-4c06da1e954d","timestamp":"2026-02-21T12:32:28.135Z"}
